  "description": "<p><u><strong>Responsibilities</strong></u></p><p>•\tCounter duties such as registration</p><p>•\tAssist clinic manager with day-to-day clinic operations.</p><p>•\tAttend to walk-in patients and phone enquiries.</p><p>•\tTo assist patients with the booking of their appointments and health screening.</p><p>•\tTo generate/ tabulate data and administrative work</p><p>•\tAny other tasks as assigned</p><p><u><strong>Requirements</strong></u></p><p>•\tMinimum GCE ‘O’ Level or equivalent</p><p>•\tPreferably with relevant working experience</p><p>•\tExcellent customer service skills and attitude</p><p>Interested candidates please send in your resume to:</p><p><u><strong>valerie@recruitexpress.com.sg</strong></u></p><p>EA Personnel: Valerie Yong Kian Fung</p><p>CEI No.: R1103704</p><p>Recruit Express Pte Ltd, EA License No.: 99C4599</p>",
